Package org.universAAL.ri.api.manager.server

Classes related to the actual servlet handling the calls to the API.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Authenticator
    Implementatino of OSGi HttpContext to be used by the Servlet.
    Base64  
    Base64.InputStream
    A Base64.InputStream will read data from another java.io.InputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    Base64.OutputStream
    A Base64.OutputStream will write data to another java.io.OutputStream, given in the constructor, and encode/decode to/from Base64 notation on the fly.
    RemoteServlet
    An HTTP Servlet that handles the calls to the Remote API server.
